                                    {
                                        "ancestorRefs": [
                                            "12",
                                            "M1201"
                                        ],
                                        "body": "The provisions of Chapters <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"#12\">12</a> through <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/texas/irc-2021/chapter/24/fuel-gas#24\">24</a> shall regulate the design, installation, maintenance, <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/texas/irc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#alteration_\">alteration</a></span> and inspection of <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/texas/irc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#mechanical_system_\">mechanical systems</a> that are permanently installed and used to <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/texas/irc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#control_limit_\">control</a> environmental conditions within buildings. These chapters shall also regulate those <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/texas/irc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#mechanical_system_\">mechanical systems</a>, system components, <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/texas/irc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#equipment_\">equipment</a></span> and <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/texas/irc-2021/chapter/2/definitions#appliance_\">appliances</a></span> specifically addressed in this code.",
